    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is a mechanically sound E46 M3 powered by the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and a 7,900 RPM redline. This example utilizes the Getrag 6-speed manual transmission for precise engagement, paired with a functional variable M differential lock. The chassis remains composed with recent subframe reinforcement and refreshed bushings, ensuring the legendary handling dynamics remain sharp. The VANOS system has been serviced, and the valvetrain maintains its signature mechanical clarity. A true driver\u2019s car with excellent throttle response and structural integrity.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
