      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 2
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle represents a fantastic opportunity for a buyer seeking a well-maintained, reliable driver. The exterior paint retains a high-gloss finish, though close inspection will reveal minor road peppering on the front bumper and a few faint surface scratches consistent with careful ownership. Inside, the cabin is a highlight: the non-smoker interior features leather seats that have been regularly treated to prevent cracking, and the carpets have been protected by floor mats since day one. All electronic components, from the responsive touchscreen interface to the heated seats and sunroof, are in full working order. Under the hood, the engine runs quietly and the transmission provides smooth, predictable shifts. We have stayed ahead of the maintenance schedule, with a recent synthetic oil change and a cooling system flush performed just 2,000 miles ago. The tires are matched Michelin Pilots with plenty of seasonal life left, and the brakes provide firm, confident stopping power. This car is mechanically sound, aesthetically pleasing, and ready for immediate delivery.",
